Quarto

Quarto enables you to weave together content and executable code into a finished document. To learn more about Quarto see https://quarto.org.

Running Code

When you click the Render button a document will be generated that includes both content and the output of embedded code. You can embed code like this:(Axtell and Munteanu 2021)

Axtell and Munteanu (2021) blah blah blah
